title: Hawkeye & Mockingbird Sketchbook (2010) #1
description: The Heroic Age is here! Jim McCann and David Lopez reunite for HAWKEYE & MOCKINGBIRD, an all-new ongoing jam-packed with action and arrows as one of Marvel’s favorite couples work alongside a superstar cast of allies to square off against classic villains and all new adversaries. Get an early look at two of the most popular Avengers in the Hawkeye & Mockingbird sketchbook on Marvel Digital Comics Unlimited! It’s your first glimpse at unreleased artwork and commentary from the creative team before HAWKEYE & MOCKINGBIRD #1 hits stores June 2nd, 2010.
